Hello!

If you need a custom value that is based on other field values, you can simply add a field like to ``ObjectType``:

```python
class ShipmentType(DjangoObjectType):
    some_dummy_field = graphene.String()

    class Meta:
        model = MyModel

    def resolve_some_dummy_field(self, info):
        return 'Hello to {user} from {model_name}-{instance_id}'.format(
            user=info.context.user.username,
