```
{
    serversById: {
        serverId: {  // server envelope POJO
          server: {  // server object Record
              config: { .. }, // server config Record
              kernelsById: {  // ew, POJO
                  kernelId: {  // kernel envelope POJO
                      kernel: { .. } // Record
                  }
              }
          }
        }
    }
}
```

Again, since we flattened the state, we don't have any `byId`'s that are nested inside `Record`'s like this, so it's less of an issue. However, I'll still find it less confusing if our whole state tree is really in Immutable-land.

